5 (c) A municipality may not annex land that is:
6 (1) in another municipality; OR
7 (2) LOCATED IN A DIFFERENT LEGISLATIVE DISTRICT THAN A
8 LEGISLATIVE DISTRICT IN WHICH THE MUNICIPALITY OR ANY PART OF THE
9 MUNICIPALITY IS LOCATED.
